{"id": 1866, "genre": 1000, "title": "生鲜的这么多种营销方式，有多少你不会买账？", "description": "现如今为了卖菜给你，你发觉电商们都用了哪些招数？哪些你觉得“嗬，我可已经看穿了”？（题图来自：Pixabay）", "record_count": 10498, "comment_count": 18, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170822155123z02OD1vRBJynu96q.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-08-24T17:00:14Z", "questions": [{"id": 2847, "title": "生鲜的这么多种营销方式，有多少你不会买账？", "content": "现如今为了卖菜给你，电商们都用了哪些招数？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 231055, "content": "返璞归真，商品名字是少数民族语言音译，包装上是小语种文字或者原住民照片", "image": "img/option/option/2017082314312040gLP8h3budFIX2j.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 231056, "content": "名字包含产地信息，几千公里之外运来（本地也有的）食材才是高贵的", "image": "img/option/option/20170823143210DWKawZ7dLrbcSyTQ.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 231057, "content": "产品详情里包含菜谱，把和烹饪有关的信息放在评论区上面", "image": "img/option/option/20170823143454eVL3PJMQRd0zsqXp.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 231058, "content": "口味丰富：板栗南瓜，椰香红豆……", "image": "img/option/option/20170823143916WZq9Ik3lgU6P8GDf.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 231060, "content": "讲述农夫自己的故事：放弃投行高年薪，选择去种菜", "image": "img/option/option/20170823144959U8HEloRKBf91QqhF.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 231061, "content": "帮你省心：把菜切好做成净菜包，把蔬果打成汁配送给你", "image": "img/option/option/20170823145409VdMWSGIkZPXavnze.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 231062, "content": "同时还是要强调少工序和原汁原味，新鲜果粒看得见！", "image": "img/option/option/20170823145536E0kWuQU5jM1S6zJN.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 231063, "content": "看不懂的名词，富含游离态氨基酸什么的", "image": "img/option/option/20170823145626OyIXU6F94Sn01lf3.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}